products.productName: Classic Cushion Garnet Solitaire Ring
products.productDescription: An intense red garnet sits in a four-prong setting on the lustrous 14k yellow gold shank. This cushion garnet solitaire ring draws attention to its simple elegance.

products.productName: Thin Shank Cushion Cut Garnet Ring With Diamond Accents
products.productDescription: A cushion garnet is mounted in a claw prong setting and captivates with its intense red hue. The shimmering diamonds on the thin shank and the gallery lend a glamorous edge to this elegant garnet solitaire ring in 14k white gold.

products.productName: Round Garnet Dangle Earrings with Diamond Halo
products.productDescription: Nestled within a glimmering halo of diamonds are round intense red garnets in prong settings. The diamond accents on the hoop lend an additional touch of elegance to these garnet dangle earrings crafted in 14k white gold.

products.productName: Classic Oval Amethyst Halo Ring with Diamond Accents
products.productDescription: The beauty of deep purple orchids is embodied in this 14k white gold amethyst halo ring. Held in a prong setting is this oval amethyst that shimmers remarkably. It is complemented by a halo of round diamonds that cascade down the shank and magnify the gemstone's charm.

products.productName: Round Amethyst Pendant with Diamond Halo
products.productDescription: Bold and beautiful are what best describe our amethyst halo pendant. A color-saturated, prong set amethyst gemstone is bordered by pave set diamonds. Handcrafted in the USA, this delightful amethyst diamond pendant is set in shimmering 14K White gold, adding further elegance to it. The heart design in solid metal gives it irresistible beauty.

products.productName: Dangling Round Amethyst and Diamond Halo Pendant
products.productDescription: Dangling from a diamond encrusted bale is a round intense purple amethyst, framed by a glittering halo of diamonds. Prong set in 14k white gold.

products.productName: Milgrain-Edged Square Aquamarine and Diamond Halo Rin
products.productDescription: Resembling the beauty of the ocean is the brilliant square aquamarine in the center, surrounded by a dazzling array of diamonds. There are shimmering diamonds on the shoulders and dainty bezel set round diamonds on the sides of the blue gemstone that sits within the halo. The intricate milgrain detailing along the edges of this 14k gold aquamarine halo ring exudes the exquisiteness of the jewels of the Victorian era.

products.productName: Bezel-Set Aquamarine Pendant with Coffee Diamond Halo
products.productDescription: Exhibiting a sophisticated and luxurious look, the round aquamarine is surrounded by a halo of coffee diamonds in a black rhodium setting. products.productName: Diamond Bloodstone Birthstone Ballerina Ring In Black Gold
products.productDescription: Sparkling diamonds surrounding a bloodstone birthstone in a lovely ballerina design will surely turn heads for a second look. Crafted in your choice of 10K, 14K or 18K solid white gold and has a black rhodium plated finish. Price displayed is for 10K white gold. Contains a 7 X 5MM prong set oval-cut genuine bloodstone gemstone, accented by 16 natural sparkling diamonds.

products.productName: Diamond Silver Bloodstone Love Knot Ring
products.productDescription: A bloodstone gemstone, in an intricate design glowing with love, is the centerpiece of this Love Knot ring. The ring contains a genuine 8MM round cut bloodstone, and is accented by 5 white round natural diamonds.

products.productName: Spiral Illusion Diamond Tennis Bracelet

products.productName: Classic Oval Emerald and Diamond Tennis Bracelet
products.productDescription: This emerald tennis bracelet with catch clasp looks luxurious in 14k yellow gold. The oval emeralds and the round diamonds are alternately prong set in a row for a mesmerizing effect.

products.productName: Akoya Cultured Pearl Bypass Ring with Trio Diamond
products.productDescription: A split shank transforming into a bypass band embraces the beautiful cultured Akoya pearl. Trios of round accent diamonds are prong set at the ends of the bypass, giving a classic look to the solitaire pearl ring. This pearl bypass ring crafted in 14k gold will emulate your love affair with all things dainty and elegant.

products.productName: Classic Freshwater Cultured Pearl Necklace
products.productDescription: White Freshwater cultured pearls are double knotted on white silk to create a 20-inch one-strand necklace. Their lustrous and smooth exterior is simply eye-catching. This Freshwater cultured pearl necklace is finished with a decorative 14k white gold clasp.

products.productName: Lab-Created Alexandrite Ring Sterling Silver
products.productDescription: A vivid round lab-created alexandrite bordered by twin lab-created white sapphires illuminates the center of this fashion jewelry ring for her. Intertwining swirls of sterling silver define the band to complete the look.

products.productName: Classic Oval Peridot Floral Halo Ring
